The place where American
teenagers meet is a mall.

00:15:45.970 --> 00:15:51.430
Magliare la palla,
Pall Mall, mall.

00:15:51.430 --> 00:16:04.250
The Cours la Reine in Paris
became as Marie de' Medici

00:16:04.250 --> 00:16:09.260
built it, who was responsible
for its construction,

00:16:09.260 --> 00:16:17.960
