Henri Lefebvre's work,

00:58:30.440 --> 00:58:35.570
the right to the town
is exemplified by that.

00:58:35.570 --> 00:58:42.440
If you have two distinct
towns, if you grow up

00:58:42.440 --> 00:58:47.920
on the wrong side
of the railroad,

00:58:47.920 --> 00:58:53.530
