your right to the town.

00:58:53.530 --> 00:58:58.540
In Paris, which becomes more and
more expensive, more and more,

00:58:58.540 --> 00:59:03.310
the great tourist center
of the world building

00:59:03.310 --> 00:59:11.380
more and more museums, artifacts
along the quay of the river,

00:59:11.380 --> 00:59:17.850
the curious quays of the
river, the competition

00:59:17.850 --> 00:59:21.330
