00:59:21.330 --> 00:59:28.170
The competition for
cities is a waste of time.

00:59:28.170 --> 00:59:32.580
The variables are too
mentally complicated, too.

00:59:32.580 --> 00:59:37.530
City planning is not a unique--
a one sort of a time exercise.

00:59:37.530 --> 00:59:39.480
The only plan I
know of a city that

00:59:39.480 --> 00:59:43.260
